Path: godot/classes/class_world2d.rst  
Summary: Properties of the World2D class, including their types and associated values.  

- canvas (RID): Reference to the canvas associated with this world.  
- direct_space_state (PhysicsDirectSpaceState2D): The direct space state for physics calculations.  
- navigation_map (RID): Reference to the navigation map used for pathfinding.  
- space (RID): Identifier for the space this world belongs to.
