Document: World2D  
Path: godot/classes/class_world2d.rst  
Summary: Properties of the World2D class including canvas, direct space state, navigation map, and physics space references.  

RID canvas  
The RID of this world's canvas resource. Used by the RenderingServer for 2D drawing.  

RID navigation_map  
The RID of this world's navigation map. Used by the NavigationServer2D.  

RID space  
The RID of this world's physics space resource. Used by the PhysicsServer2D for 2D physics, treating it as both a space and an area.  

PhysicsDirectSpaceState2D direct_space_state  
Direct access to the world's physics 2D space state. Used for querying current and potential collisions. Note: When using multi-threaded physics, access is limited to Node._physics_process() in the main thread.